<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">
<h2>OPD Patient Appointment</h2>
<hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
<div class="clear"></div>
This screen captures the OPD Patient Appointments for the out patient. This screen will be used for maintaining Patient appointments information for all clinical departments. This screen will contain information of time Slot, Slots Available, HIN, Patient Name, Service no, Patient Name, Mobile no, Age, Sex and Doctor Name
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/app_opdpatientappointment.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>
<span class="title">Department:</span><br />
    User can select the department from the given list, this will come from department screen, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Appointment Date: </span> 
    <br />User can select Appointment date based on Department setup based on department time the slots will display and it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Slots Available:  </span> 
    <br />Based on user Department selection and Appointment date all slots will display, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Appointment Criteria: </span> 
    <br />Appointment Criteria contains 3 types 1) Service No 2) HIN No 3) None
          Service No: If user knows service no then all service details will fetch automatically from the data base.
          HIN No: If user knows HIN No then all service details will fetch automatically from the data base.
          None: if patient is new patient then user can enter service no, Service Person Name, Relation, Patient Name, Age, Sex and Mobile Number It cannot have null.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Service No:</span> 
    <br />User can write service no details, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Service Person Name:</span> 
    <br />User can write service person name details, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
     <span class="title">HIN No:</span> 
    <br />Allregistered Patients will get HIN No, if user knows HIN number then user can write HIN No and it can't remain blank.
    <br />
     <span class="title">Relation:</span> 
    <br />User can select patient relation from the list, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
     <span class="title">Patient Name:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient name it is enterable, it can't remain blank.
     <br />
     <span class="title">Mobile No:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient Mobile Number, it can't remain blank.
     <br />
     <span class="title">Sex:</span> 
    <br />User can select patient Sex from the list, it can't remain blank.
     <br />
     <span class="title">Age:</span> 
    <br />User can write patient age, it can't remain blank.
    <br />
     <span class="title">Doctorâ€™s Name:</span> 
    <br />User can select the doctor name from the given list, this will come from employee screen, it can remain blank.
    <br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Submit button user can save the data.  
<br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data.


</p>
